[10:13.26]	And replant Henry in his former state.
[10:16.06]QUEEN MARGARET	Warwick, these words have turn'd my hate to love;
[10:19.51]	And I forgive and quite forget old faults,
[10:22.56]	And joy that thou becomest King Henry's friend.
